	dprr:hasNoteText "A Praetor Manlius, perhaps A. Manlius Torquatus (RE no. 74), was defeated by the slaves in Sicily (Flor. 2.7.7; cf. Frontin. Str. 3.5.3; see 139, Praetors, and note 1)." .
